name: 30 day Fitness Planner
description: No time to organize or decide what to do and when to do it? No problem, with Fitness Planner it will be mapped out for you.  All that is needed from you is to answer a few questions and provide a 5 day schedule of the daily necessities you MUST do, everything else will be taken care of.  A unique plan will be designed just for you to include what exercise to perform and the duration.   You can't get outside-no problem, You can't run-no problem, You can't lift weights-no problem...the Fitness Planner will resolve all of that.

name: 5 day meal plan
description:
Tired of not knowing where to begin to plan meals for the week.  Wanna Lick will help with that.  You will be provided with a total of 25 meals that can be used for 5 days.  It is recommended to eat 5 small meals a day with a time frame of 2-3 hours in between.  

These meals are not limited to just 5 days, interchange them and you can go on for weeks on end.

All recipes will come the nutritional facts.

Be Fit, Be Strong, Be Healthy!
Thanks

name: Juicing Recipes
description:
10 juicing recipes that will rev up your energy and satisfy your taste buds.  You simply provide your favorite fruit and leave the rest to Wanna Lick.  The outcome will be heavenly.

When placing your order simply, advise which fruit you want as your base fruit.  Recipes will be emailed once payment has been confirmed.

Be Healthy, Be Fit, Be Strong!
